Pizza Sales Report:
This pizza have verious pizza products. 2015 sale of all pizzas and category. Create the Dashboard include below KPIs, Charts and filters.
KPIs:
  1)Total revenue.
  2)Total Orders.
  3)Total pizza Sold.
  4)Avg Order value.
  5)Avg pizzas per order.

Charts:
  1)Total Orders by Day name.
  2)Total Orders by month name.
  3)Total revenue by pizza category.
  4)Total revenue by pizza size.
  5)Total Pizzas Sold by pizza category.
  6)Total pizzas sales by Revenue.

Filter:
  1)Pizza category.
